Title: Calimucho
Director: Eugenie Jansen, Rosa Fontein, Michel Kapteijns
Writer: Natasha Gerson (story and screenplay), Rogier de Blok
Actors: Evelyne Bougliogne, Tarek Hannoudi, Joshy Huppertz, Manfred Huppertz
Plot: A young woman needs to make a choice between her family and her personal freedom in a financially unstable family circus.
